ygData.subject: Re: New, with a million questions
ygData.msgSnippet: Peeps = a slang term for people. Twinking = when a higher level character gives a lower level character stuff that they would not be albe to get
ygData.messageBody:
Peeps = a slang term for people.<br>Twinking =
when a higher level character gives a lower level
character stuff that they would not be albe to get
themselves.<br>Any non pvp server is good to start on. You just have
to make some friends.<br>On each server your allowed
up to 8 characters. You can also play on as many
servers as you want.<br>The cat people will be out in
december not sure the exact date but I know its in
december. And they will be albe to be bards, warriors,
shaman, beastmasters. Not sure what else
though.<br><br><br>Ommuien<br>52 Chanter<br>Bertox
